snippet.title: ACAAICOLA
snippet.description:
The presentations on this YouTube channel are provided as a service by Children's Mercy Hospital and the American College of Allergy, Asthma & Immunology ("ACAAI").

Presentation materials are not to be relied on as professional opinions or consultations and are not intended to constitute practice guidelines or to supplant physician judgment with respect to particular individuals or situations.

The views expressed in the presentations are those of the individual presenters only. ACAAI makes no warranty, guarantee, or representation as to the accuracy or sufficiency of the presentations and assumes no responsibility or liability in connection with the use or misuse of the information provided therein. 

Presentations are given live every Monday and Friday from 10-12 Central Time.
